
'''= a local Swedish political party, and represents an experiment with direct democracy in Vallentuna, a Stockholm suburb in Sweden. Representatives act based on the results of local meetings with constituents.''' 

URL = http://demoex.net/

=Description=

"It is an association for direct democracy via Internet that makes it possible for anyone to be active in the local government's debates (but only members have the rights to vote). Since 2003 Demoex has had a commission in the local parliament of Vallentuna, having acquired the first direct democracy mandate ever in Europe."
(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Demoex)


